WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

2
00:01:50.806 --> 00:01:52.057
- Hello?
- Mr. Lin?

3
00:01:52.553 --> 00:01:54.435
Your daughter's condition
is deteriorating.

4
00:01:54.437 --> 00:01:56.773
How can that be?
She was fine earlier today.

5
00:01:57.429 --> 00:01:59.364
She heals faster than usual.

6
00:02:00.065 --> 00:02:03.143
However.... the leukemia
cells accumulated again...

7
00:02:03.584 --> 00:02:05.207
so her condition has deteriorated.

8
00:02:05.209 --> 00:02:08.634
But Xixi is strong-minded.

9
00:02:08.635 --> 00:02:10.526
Before she went into the coma.

10
00:02:10.528 --> 00:02:13.573
she told everyone you promised
to be there for her birthday.

11
00:02:13.920 --> 00:02:14.622
Peter.

12
00:02:14.921 --> 00:02:16.329
you must save her!

13
00:02:16.823 --> 00:02:19.959
I'm on my way. Please do your best.

14
00:02:52.656 --> 00:02:53.949
Move. move! Sorry!

15
00:03:19.976 --> 00:03:22.541
- Hello?
- Officer Lin. we have a problem.

16
00:03:22.543 --> 00:03:23.273
What do you mean?

17
00:03:23.275 --> 00:03:25.152
Our witness protection
has been compromised.

18
00:03:25.317 --> 00:03:28.776
We just lost contact with our men.
I'm afraid our witness has been exposed.

19
00:03:29.087 --> 00:03:31.423
Witness Protection is Grade A.
What are you telling me?

20
00:03:31.425 --> 00:03:32.324
What happened?

21
00:03:32.326 --> 00:03:35.630
I'm not sure. but HQ has confirmed
the identity of the witness.

22
00:03:35.632 --> 00:03:39.344
It's Dr. James. the reclusive
geneticist who recently defected.

23
00:03:40.163 --> 00:03:40.912
For five years.

24
00:03:40.914 --> 00:03:45.102
he's been secretly working for the biggest
arms dealer. researching biochemical weapons.

25
00:03:46.051 --> 00:03:50.796
A week ago. his bio-roid went haywire
and killed everyone in the lab.

26
00:03:50.798 --> 00:03:55.595
The arms dealer was brutally
killed and his assets seized.

27
00:03:55.597 --> 00:03:57.224
Bio-roid? What research?

28
00:03:57.580 --> 00:03:59.266
We don't know the details.

29
00:03:59.268 --> 00:04:02.396
It's some kind of special force
exposed to nuclear radiation.

30
00:05:56.976 --> 00:05:57.893
Let's go.

31
00:06:19.199 --> 00:06:20.242
Xixi...

32
00:06:24.288 --> 00:06:25.122
Go.

33
00:07:38.027 --> 00:07:38.987
Come on. get in.

34
00:07:54.316 --> 00:07:55.276
Take cover!

35
00:08:08.383 --> 00:08:10.115
- Get back!
- Back!

36
00:08:17.811 --> 00:08:18.770
Get back!

37
00:08:52.909 --> 00:08:54.661
- Cover me.
- Okay.

38
00:09:11.642 --> 00:09:12.643
Careful!

39
00:09:33.937 --> 00:09:36.993
Susan. I'll distract them.
You go for the car!

40
00:09:38.148 --> 00:09:39.149
Officer Lin!

41
00:09:50.076 --> 00:09:52.454
- Get Dr. James out of here!
- What about you?

42
00:09:53.032 --> 00:09:54.753
Just go! Protect the witness first.

43
00:09:54.755 --> 00:09:56.215
- Okay.
- Flash bomb.

44
00:10:02.595 --> 00:10:04.687
You. follow me.

45
00:10:15.505 --> 00:10:18.019
- We've got to get to the car!
- Johnny. hang in there.

46
00:10:18.021 --> 00:10:18.855
I'm okay.

47
00:10:33.703 --> 00:10:36.052
- Susan. are you okay?
- Okay for now.

48
00:11:37.893 --> 00:11:39.061
No!

49
00:11:43.481 --> 00:11:44.357
Don't do that!

50
00:11:49.154 --> 00:11:50.405
Don't do that!

51
00:12:13.778 --> 00:12:15.696
Go! Come on!

52
00:12:20.527 --> 00:12:21.931
No! Doctor!

53
00:13:07.284 --> 00:13:08.997
The doctor has been shot.

54
00:13:10.872 --> 00:13:13.146
Requesting backup.

55
00:13:18.957 --> 00:13:19.958
Repeat...

56
00:13:20.133 --> 00:13:22.260
the doctor...

57
00:13:27.165 --> 00:13:29.542
Requesting backup.

58
00:15:34.959 --> 00:15:36.419
Papa. Papa.

59
00:29:15.282 --> 00:29:16.617
Rick was a pervert.

60
00:29:17.113 --> 00:29:19.198
Why was he obsessed with this girl?

61
00:33:38.295 --> 00:33:41.504
Wow. that was a hell of a punch.
You're a credit to us Chinese.

62
00:33:41.506 --> 00:33:43.300
And you know I helped. right?

63
00:33:44.115 --> 00:33:45.116
Thank you.

64
00:33:45.636 --> 00:33:47.137
Well. I have to go now.

65
00:33:47.888 --> 00:33:49.640
I'm Leeson. What's your name?

66
00:43:02.036 --> 00:43:03.037
Let's go!

67
00:43:49.989 --> 00:43:51.074
Shut the door.

68
00:43:56.970 --> 00:43:58.221
We've met before.

69
00:43:59.392 --> 00:44:01.922
- Oh. it's you.
- What are you doing here?

70
00:44:01.924 --> 00:44:04.137
- I followed you.
- Why'd you do that?

71
00:44:04.139 --> 00:44:06.560
I was kidding. Hurry up!

72
00:44:12.921 --> 00:44:13.881
So who are you?

73
00:44:16.486 --> 00:44:18.723
- Are you a gangster?
- Excuse me?

74
00:44:18.725 --> 00:44:21.159
You're always fighting.

75
00:44:24.816 --> 00:44:26.192
Hey. wait!

76
00:44:28.611 --> 00:44:31.114
Come on. relax. I was kidding.

77
00:44:32.274 --> 00:44:33.400
Don't go.

78
00:44:33.734 --> 00:44:34.610
Come on.

79
00:44:34.934 --> 00:44:36.602
Let's go for dinner tonight.

80
00:44:38.246 --> 00:44:40.039
I think you should change your pants.

81
00:44:42.912 --> 00:44:44.091
Oh. yeah.

82
00:44:44.711 --> 00:44:45.712
Well. yeah.

83
00:44:46.254 --> 00:44:47.130
Whatever.

84
00:44:47.881 --> 00:44:50.842
I'm warning you.
If you follow me again. then I'll...

85
00:44:52.742 --> 00:44:55.947
I said I was kidding.
This was just a coincidence. all right?

86
00:44:57.801 --> 00:45:00.059
Hey!

87
00:45:00.606 --> 00:45:02.442
Not even a thank you for saving you?

88
00:45:02.899 --> 00:45:04.437
You know what. lady?

89
00:45:04.439 --> 00:45:05.832
You're just crazy!

90
00:46:15.927 --> 00:46:16.803
Come on.

91
00:46:27.505 --> 00:46:28.840
You followed me.

92
00:46:29.709 --> 00:46:33.004
What the hell are you talking about?
I think you followed me.

93
00:46:33.481 --> 00:46:35.149
And who just got you in. huh?

94
00:46:35.846 --> 00:46:36.847
Whatever.

95
00:46:38.533 --> 00:46:40.284
You can't... Not that way!

96
00:46:52.876 --> 00:46:54.795
It's a maze in here. Where are you going?

97
00:46:58.689 --> 00:46:59.565
What's your name?

98
00:47:00.805 --> 00:47:01.806
Gangster.

99
00:47:03.158 --> 00:47:05.626
Come on. You know I was kidding yesterday.

100
00:47:05.628 --> 00:47:06.594
Yours?

101
00:47:07.018 --> 00:47:10.313
Huh? Don't you remember?
It's Leeson.

102
00:47:19.183 --> 00:47:21.034
- It's my stage name.
- Stolen?

103
00:47:21.571 --> 00:47:22.614
It was not.

104
00:47:24.871 --> 00:47:25.747
I found it

105
00:47:26.755 --> 00:47:28.423
You sure don't look like a Salaami.

106
00:47:35.252 --> 00:47:36.503
What are you after?

107
00:47:38.050 --> 00:47:40.343
What are you looking for? Huh?

108
00:47:59.328 --> 00:48:01.197
Just stay here. and no more fights.

109
00:48:01.624 --> 00:48:03.410
Please just stay there. okay?

110
00:48:04.611 --> 00:48:06.071
Salaami.

111
00:51:03.710 --> 00:51:04.544
Look out!

112
00:52:18.733 --> 00:52:20.276
Nancy's on the second floor.

113
00:56:27.246 --> 00:56:29.623
Hey! Over here!

114
00:57:19.173 --> 00:57:21.509
Mister. who are you to her?

115
00:57:21.925 --> 00:57:22.843
Shut up.

116
00:57:43.085 --> 00:57:45.776
Wow. nice place. Is it...

117
00:57:45.778 --> 00:57:46.696
Hey.

118
00:57:47.484 --> 00:57:48.860
- What the hell?
- Be quiet.

119
00:57:49.854 --> 00:57:50.813
Let go of me.

120
00:57:58.295 --> 00:57:59.544
- Go.
- Where?

121
00:57:59.546 --> 00:58:00.506
- Down there.
- No way.

122
00:58:01.073 --> 00:58:03.826
You trying to get rid of me?
Well. I won't go quietly.

123
00:58:04.865 --> 00:58:07.028
What the hell is this place. huh?

124
00:58:08.465 --> 00:58:09.472
Take it easy.

125
00:58:12.840 --> 00:58:16.995
Who are you? What do you do for a living?

126
00:58:20.303 --> 00:58:22.937
Do you really need to do that? Huh?

127
00:58:23.423 --> 00:58:24.341
What the hell?

128
00:58:29.598 --> 00:58:31.141
What was that thing anyhow?

129
00:58:35.269 --> 00:58:36.270
It's a time bomb.

130
00:58:36.787 --> 00:58:39.540
Tell me.
why have you been following Nancy?

131
00:58:41.004 --> 00:58:42.004
You've got to be kidding.

132
00:58:42.834 --> 00:58:44.745
You don't have to kill me to get my girl.

133
00:58:44.747 --> 00:58:48.387
Hey. I can't help it
if I'm super charming.

134
00:58:49.263 --> 00:58:51.223
You're not a student at the university.

135
00:58:51.714 --> 00:58:54.726
The ladyboy at Rick's place. It was you.

136
00:58:54.728 --> 00:58:56.271
Yes. it's true.

137
00:58:56.771 --> 00:58:59.107
But what does any of this
have to do with Nancy?

138
00:58:59.664 --> 00:59:02.173
All I did was get back
what was mine to begin with.

139
00:59:02.175 --> 00:59:03.385
What belongs to you?

140
00:59:04.319 --> 00:59:07.101
- What is it?
- Things that belong to the rich.

141
00:59:07.103 --> 00:59:08.688
I'm like Robin Hood. okay?

142
00:59:09.494 --> 00:59:10.328
It's stealing.

143
00:59:10.776 --> 00:59:13.529
You're a lazy young boy.
You're just a thief.

144
00:59:13.746 --> 00:59:16.415
Rick's a thief anyway. And he's a dick.

145
00:59:20.470 --> 00:59:22.347
What does that have to do with Nancy?

146
00:59:23.505 --> 00:59:27.426
When I was going through Rick's safe.
Nancy's library pass was in there.

147
00:59:27.840 --> 00:59:29.217
I was curious about her.

148
00:59:30.093 --> 00:59:32.095
And then she just captivated me.

149
00:59:32.560 --> 00:59:34.729
And I fell... in love.

150
00:59:39.402 --> 00:59:40.653
I've told you everything.

151
00:59:41.166 --> 00:59:44.377
So would you please remove the bomb now?

152
00:59:44.629 --> 00:59:45.838
Vitamin B.

153
00:59:47.237 --> 00:59:48.947
Good for your health and hangovers.

154
00:59:50.521 --> 00:59:51.814
Who has a hangover?

155
00:59:52.158 --> 00:59:53.324
You think you fooled me?

156
00:59:53.608 --> 00:59:56.033
I could tell it was you under that mask.

157
00:59:56.035 --> 00:59:59.202
Don't walk away.
Who do you think you are. Spider-Man?

158
00:59:59.917 --> 01:00:02.169
Until I check your identity.
you'll have to stay here.

159
01:00:03.712 --> 01:00:04.588
Hey!

160
01:00:05.267 --> 01:00:06.310
Let me out!

161
01:00:08.525 --> 01:00:13.055
Officer Lin. the evidence you acquired proves
transactions between Rick and the witch.

162
01:00:13.057 --> 01:00:16.683
For two years. the witch has been
selling Rick Nancy's therapy videos.

163
01:00:16.685 --> 01:00:19.601
Clearly. Rick based his novel
off these recordings.

164
01:00:19.603 --> 01:00:20.729
That's what I thought.

165
01:00:21.522 --> 01:00:23.690
Oh. I just sent you a sound file...

166
01:00:24.483 --> 01:00:25.860
Find out who this guy is.

167
01:02:30.337 --> 01:02:31.171
Oh. hey.

168
01:02:31.902 --> 01:02:34.029
How long are you gonna
keep me locked up here?

169
01:02:35.000 --> 01:02:37.002
I have human rights. Huh?

170
01:02:37.868 --> 01:02:41.414
I'll pee if you don't let me go.
Okay. you asked for it.

171
01:02:46.763 --> 01:02:49.069
Can you give me
water and food. please?

172
01:02:49.071 --> 01:02:52.074
I'm so dehydrated. I can't even pee.

173
01:04:00.157 --> 01:04:01.950
Hello? Nancy's gone.

174
01:04:02.466 --> 01:04:04.260
She just got on a plane to Xingan.

175
01:04:05.129 --> 01:04:06.506
I think it's happening now.

176
01:04:07.390 --> 01:04:09.463
I'm going to look for her.
I'll call you from the airport.

177
01:04:09.464 --> 01:04:12.627
What happened? Release me.
Look. I can help you.

178
01:04:13.628 --> 01:04:16.006
Whatever your game is. stay away from her.

179
01:04:16.488 --> 01:04:18.418
This is more serious than you know.

180
01:04:18.420 --> 01:04:21.039
- I want to protect her.
- She doesn't need you.

181
01:04:21.041 --> 01:04:24.127
Here's the key. This door will open
automatically tomorrow.

182
01:04:24.306 --> 01:04:26.683
There's food and drink in the room.
You won't starve.

183
01:04:27.726 --> 01:04:29.811
That's dog food. There.

184
01:04:30.377 --> 01:04:31.420
Train your arms.

185
01:04:32.264 --> 01:04:33.099
Hey!

186
01:04:33.482 --> 01:04:35.150
This is an illegal detention.

187
01:04:35.921 --> 01:04:37.089
Don't go!

188
01:05:50.578 --> 01:05:51.412
Earthquake?

189
01:06:10.046 --> 01:06:11.005
Officer Lin...

190
01:06:11.556 --> 01:06:12.724
your new identity.

191
01:06:15.478 --> 01:06:16.855
The old files...

192
01:06:18.269 --> 01:06:19.896
state you and Xixi died.

193
01:06:23.425 --> 01:06:24.843
And Dr. James's body...

194
01:06:25.664 --> 01:06:26.957
we had it taken care of.

195
01:06:28.700 --> 01:06:31.054
He managed to save Xixi
with a mechanical heart and

196
01:06:31.056 --> 01:06:33.627
bio-engineered blood that Andre
tried to steal before he died.

197
01:06:35.047 --> 01:06:39.037
Inside Xixi's body are the
bio-engineered genes of Dr. James.

198
01:06:40.275 --> 01:06:41.985
So far. no sign of rejection.

199
01:06:42.765 --> 01:06:46.624
The bio-engineered blood in
Xixi's body is super regenerative.

200
01:06:48.709 --> 01:06:50.877
However. when she wakes up...

201
01:06:52.657 --> 01:06:54.576
her old memories will be gone.

202
01:06:58.179 --> 01:06:59.264
Memories of you.

203
01:07:06.885 --> 01:07:10.597
Was the thing I blew up the bio-roid?

204
01:07:12.541 --> 01:07:13.459
Yeah.

205
01:07:14.939 --> 01:07:17.060
He was an experimental subject.

206
01:07:17.062 --> 01:07:21.191
Dr. James called him Andre.
His body wasn't recovered at the scene.

207
01:07:22.198 --> 01:07:23.450
We're still searching.

208
01:07:25.393 --> 01:07:26.310
Susan...

209
01:07:27.008 --> 01:07:27.842
Yes. sir.

210
01:07:28.521 --> 01:07:30.156
Can you do me a favor?

211
01:07:30.158 --> 01:07:30.992
Of course.

212
01:07:31.154 --> 01:07:36.039
Take her to an orphanage in Australia.
to Director Isabella.

213
01:07:36.982 --> 01:07:39.735
Andre will definitely come back.

214
01:07:40.522 --> 01:07:42.666
I don't want Xixi to be involved.

215
01:07:42.668 --> 01:07:45.045
As long as she lives.

216
01:07:46.076 --> 01:07:48.912
I will protect her as a stranger.

217
01:07:50.006 --> 01:07:53.766
As her father.
her safety is all I ask for.

218
01:08:09.377 --> 01:08:12.005
Officer Lin.
if Xixi's memories are coming back.

219
01:08:12.007 --> 01:08:15.135
are they hers or are they Dr. James's?

220
01:08:15.730 --> 01:08:17.441
That's what I worry about.

221
01:08:18.069 --> 01:08:20.629
Oh. yeah. what about the guy
I asked you to check out?

222
01:08:20.631 --> 01:08:22.549
His name is Leeson.

223
01:08:22.919 --> 01:08:24.697
He lives in Sydney.

224
01:08:24.699 --> 01:08:28.832
In 2011. he traveled to Korea.
the US. and Japan.

225
01:08:28.834 --> 01:08:30.420
Then he returned to Sydney.

226
01:08:30.422 --> 01:08:33.676
He has no work records.
no family we could find.

227
01:08:34.142 --> 01:08:36.690
He was arrested for theft a year ago

228
01:08:36.692 --> 01:08:39.152
and was released due to lack of evidence.

229
01:08:40.176 --> 01:08:41.469
What did he steal?

230
01:08:41.858 --> 01:08:44.319
We don't know. His file is classified.

231
01:08:44.908 --> 01:08:47.410
We are still communicating
with Australian police.

232
01:08:49.157 --> 01:08:51.201
He's not a normal thief.

233
01:08:51.960 --> 01:08:53.462
No. We don't think so either.

234
01:08:56.133 --> 01:08:59.515
Oh. we're losing Xixi's signal.
I think we should separate.

235
01:08:59.517 --> 01:09:02.145
Okay. That's a good idea.
I'll go back to headquarters.

236
01:09:22.151 --> 01:09:25.279
We will do everything we can
to have your identity restored.

237
01:09:31.071 --> 01:09:35.325
If I can find Xixi. I just want to
have a beautiful life with her.

238
01:09:36.557 --> 01:09:37.433
See you.

239
01:09:37.857 --> 01:09:38.547
Hey...

240
01:09:40.211 --> 01:09:41.128
Good luck. Officer.

241
01:12:00.776 --> 01:12:04.572
Papa. you've been with me all along.

242
01:12:45.483 --> 01:12:47.942
Xixi!

243
01:15:19.726 --> 01:15:22.560
It worked! Oh. my God.

244
01:15:43.267 --> 01:15:45.353
Hey. that was the wrong car.

245
01:15:45.355 --> 01:15:46.398
How did you get out?

246
01:15:47.071 --> 01:15:49.031
A fitness machine is no match for me.

247
01:15:49.746 --> 01:15:51.861
If you're that good. help me to find them.

248
01:15:51.863 --> 01:15:55.968
Pay attention. I am helping.
We just need this

249
01:16:00.705 --> 01:16:01.539
Hang on.

250
01:16:05.407 --> 01:16:06.366
There.

251
01:16:08.022 --> 01:16:09.440
Good job. Go back to Sydney.

252
01:16:09.719 --> 01:16:12.430
What? You're not very polite.

253
01:16:12.909 --> 01:16:15.187
- Go on. then.
- Hello? They've got Nancy.

254
01:16:15.189 --> 01:16:16.974
I'm sending you a location.

255
01:16:16.976 --> 01:16:18.102
- Got it.
- Okay.

256
01:16:44.045 --> 01:16:45.213
Honey. look.

257
01:16:45.825 --> 01:16:47.118
Aliens from space.

258
01:18:10.174 --> 01:18:11.175
Let's roll!

259
01:18:14.431 --> 01:18:15.307
Turn here.

260
01:18:27.273 --> 01:18:28.858
- Susan?
- Get in.

261
01:19:13.319 --> 01:19:14.153
That's pretty good.

262
01:19:15.237 --> 01:19:17.281
I don't want to see more people get hurt.

263
01:19:17.559 --> 01:19:20.187
Our intel told us
they would hit this vault.

264
01:19:20.780 --> 01:19:25.467
And we know their suits
are susceptible to gas.

265
01:20:02.021 --> 01:20:02.932
What's this?

266
01:20:03.797 --> 01:20:05.803
This is all that we found in the safe.

267
01:20:05.805 --> 01:20:07.390
- Nothing else.
- Just a camera.

268
01:20:07.671 --> 01:20:08.797
Okay. Thank you.

269
01:21:33.566 --> 01:21:36.027
If Andre got his hands on the lab records.

270
01:21:36.392 --> 01:21:38.645
he can make an army of bio-roids.

271
01:21:39.410 --> 01:21:41.662
Oh... That's horrifying.

272
01:21:41.967 --> 01:21:43.677
We can't let Andre get this.

273
01:21:44.184 --> 01:21:45.497
According to our intel.

274
01:21:45.499 --> 01:21:49.045
Andre had a secret deal
with a prominent arms dealer.

275
01:21:49.565 --> 01:21:52.901
I bet this is what they
were working on together.

276
01:21:53.539 --> 01:21:56.167
This is the only thing we have
we can trade for Nancy.

277
01:21:56.538 --> 01:21:59.016
No matter what. he won't release Nancy.

278
01:21:59.601 --> 01:22:02.645
Officer Lin.
if Andre was hurt 13 years ago.

279
01:22:02.647 --> 01:22:05.656
then what he needs is a procedure.

280
01:22:05.658 --> 01:22:11.146
That means that what he needs more than
anything is Nancy's blood to save himself.

281
01:22:11.986 --> 01:22:14.638
The two things he needs
are Nancy and that camera.

282
01:22:15.328 --> 01:22:18.372
While we have the camera.
Nancy should be safe.

283
01:22:19.233 --> 01:22:21.985
We don't have much time.
We have to find Andre.

284
01:22:25.256 --> 01:22:26.299
I have an idea.

285
01:22:26.858 --> 01:22:28.235
- The camera.
- Oh.

286
01:22:34.145 --> 01:22:35.855
Take this camera straight to headquarters.

287
01:25:55.471 --> 01:25:56.513
What's that?

288
01:25:57.848 --> 01:25:59.391
- Quiet down.
- Hmm.

289
01:26:02.811 --> 01:26:03.854
Second floor.

290
01:26:04.399 --> 01:26:05.275
Let's go.

291
01:27:04.664 --> 01:27:06.205
How do we open this?

292
01:27:06.791 --> 01:27:08.294
How do we get in?

293
01:27:10.229 --> 01:27:11.230
Get back!

294
01:27:47.436 --> 01:27:48.312
Fuck you!

295
01:30:24.003 --> 01:30:25.388
It's me! It's me!

296
01:30:25.390 --> 01:30:27.392
I was trying to help.
but my gun was out of power.

297
01:31:14.331 --> 01:31:16.208
On three. we attack.

298
01:31:16.646 --> 01:31:18.105
Hey! I haven't even counted!

299
01:34:00.564 --> 01:34:01.823
Come and help me!

300
01:34:01.825 --> 01:34:02.659
Okay.

301
01:34:31.423 --> 01:34:33.216
Officer Lin! Are you okay?

302
01:34:33.707 --> 01:34:36.335
- Let's go!
- It's gonna explode! Run!

303
01:34:37.325 --> 01:34:39.035
Run! Hurry!

304
01:34:57.634 --> 01:34:59.260
Leeson!

305
01:35:00.807 --> 01:35:04.227
Go! Go. hurry!

306
01:35:34.432 --> 01:35:37.244
It's going to crash!
Get the parachutes!

307
01:35:37.246 --> 01:35:38.706
- Okay
- Hurry!

308
01:35:40.347 --> 01:35:41.389
Papa.

309
01:35:41.723 --> 01:35:42.682
Papa's fine.

310
01:35:43.547 --> 01:35:44.464
Don't worry.

311
01:35:45.185 --> 01:35:47.270
Susan! Strap her in!

312
01:35:47.604 --> 01:35:49.105
Don't ever leave me again.

313
01:36:02.934 --> 01:36:04.769
Get her out of here!

314
01:36:21.570 --> 01:36:26.737
Papa. Papa. When I get well.
will you take me on the merry-go-round?

315
01:38:04.324 --> 01:38:06.576
Papa! Papa!

316
01:38:06.987 --> 01:38:09.364
Susan. do something. Save him.

317
01:38:10.064 --> 01:38:12.411
Pull the black handle
on your left when I say.

318
01:38:12.413 --> 01:38:13.247
Okay.

319
01:38:16.819 --> 01:38:17.695
NOW!

320
01:39:03.925 --> 01:39:04.759
Papa!

321
01:39:05.176 --> 01:39:06.010
Xixi!

322
01:39:12.934 --> 01:39:14.811
Papa's fine. It's okay.

323
01:39:17.309 --> 01:39:21.317
- Sir. the lab records are missing.
- What? The camera's missing.

324
01:39:30.535 --> 01:39:31.953
Hi!

325
01:39:58.521 --> 01:40:00.106
- I'm dizzy.
- Papa. let's try that one.

326
01:40:00.190 --> 01:40:01.441
- Which one?
- Over there.

327
01:40:01.977 --> 01:40:04.313
- That one.
- No. no. no. my heart can't.

328
01:40:04.903 --> 01:40:07.739
- Please.
- Xixi. I'll go. I like that one.

329
01:40:07.822 --> 01:40:08.571
All right.

330
01:40:08.573 --> 01:40:11.325
You go sit down over there.
I'm gonna get some ice cream.

331
01:40:11.576 --> 01:40:13.552
- Oh. I want chocolate.
- Okay.

332
01:40:13.554 --> 01:40:15.181
- I need to sit down.
- Right here.

333
01:40:15.872 --> 01:40:17.916
I was shooting like this...

334
01:40:19.083 --> 01:40:20.668
I knew you'd be dizzy.

335
01:40:24.464 --> 01:40:25.965
It's just like a dream. Pinch me.

336
01:40:27.824 --> 01:40:30.285
I won't do that. You'll wake up.

337
01:40:30.761 --> 01:40:33.347
You've been waiting for this for 13 years.

338
01:40:33.688 --> 01:40:34.898
I'm happy for you.

339
01:40:45.554 --> 01:40:47.931
Officer Lin. headquarters just called.

340
01:40:47.933 --> 01:40:49.560
We know Leeson's true identity.

341
01:40:49.966 --> 01:40:52.232
His real name is Choi Kyung-ho.

342
01:40:55.328 --> 01:40:59.916
His father was the arms dealer
killed 13 years ago by Andre.

343
01:41:00.672 --> 01:41:03.217
So his real motivation was to get revenge

344
01:41:04.154 --> 01:41:05.785
and take back his family assets.

345
01:41:05.787 --> 01:41:08.095
All I did was get back
what was mine to begin with.

346
01:41:10.123 --> 01:41:13.042
When his family was killed.
he was traveling abroad.

347
01:41:13.428 --> 01:41:14.596
So he survived.

348
01:41:15.741 --> 01:41:20.491
Coincidentally. he and Xixi grew
up together in the orphanage.

348
01:41:21.305 --> 01:42:21.771
